#  M27 — DOMAIN RETENTION & CROSS-MAPPING
#  Not mere pluggability: the organism INTERNALIZES and COMPRESSES domains and
#  RETAINS all of them; in use a domain is decompressed. Across retained
#  domains, their mapped VARIANCES let them correct against and communicate
#  with each other (pulling OrgInfecticon's function in to mediate). The cross-
#  domain currency is invariants / variance / fingerprints / distributions
#  ("invariants everywhere — Chiron power"): the signature machinery + crystal
#  lattice are the retention-and-cross-mapping core.
